                    <span>If you are preparing for your PMP Certification Exam, you should invest in this book.  Don't pay attention to any negative reviews.  This book was critical in helping me pass the exam - which I did easily (90%).  The book presents material which is most important on the exam and helps you to understand the dry PMBOK material very easily.  I found the activities to be very useful and the questions in the book will be very similar to the real exam. Good luck!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Ok book</div>
