                    <span>I read the Guide to the PMBOK two/more times. I completed the online course and reviewed the material two/more times. I read other project management books. These were all good for broad project management knowledge.
<br />
<br />But if you are serious about passing the exam, buy and study this book now! Good luck!</span>
                  
              
